## Stack

- **Framework:** Next.js 15+ App Router, React 19, TypeScript
- **Data:** Supabase (Postgres + RLS + Storage)
- **UI:** Tailwind CSS 4, shadcn/ui, Radix
- **AI:** Vercel AI SDK + OpenAI
- **Export:** pptxgenjs
- **Jobs:** Inngest | **Email:** Resend | **Billing:** Stripe

## Conventions

- Server Components by default; `'use client'` only when needed
- All data access scoped by `org_id`; never bypass RLS
- Types in `src/types/`; shared logic in `src/lib/`
- Validate API input with Zod; return typed errors
- Slide contract lives in `src/types/slide.ts` — do not diverge

## Next.js note

Read `node_modules/next/dist/docs/` before using unfamiliar APIs. This project may use newer Next.js conventions than your training data.
